data.description: The Calder Place Cottage you have been looking for, It features  2 living areas , 2 dining areas, and 3 large bedrooms. The galley kitchen is very chirming with granite countertops, updated appliances and ample storage. The large primary suite has several closets and a large bath/dressing area that makes you wan to retreat to your own  room to relax. Large backyard with covered deck and patio plus a 2 car garage. Call to see it ASAP!
